---
title: Bison and Ricotta Meatballs with Fresh Linguine
description: Rich bison and fluffy ricotta combine for the ultimate Italian-style meatball dinner. Twirl fresh linguine through herby tomato sauce for flavours that will have you convinced you've taken a trip to Rome!
